### Register user baru
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Refresh token (ganti refresh_token dengan hasil login)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

### Logout (ganti refresh_token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

### Profile (ganti access_token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN

### Google login
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/google/login

### GitHub login
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/github/login

### Admin dashboard (ganti access_token admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN
